  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed; structured level evidence is documented for 12 factors. The assessment team concluded that the overall credibility package supports acceptance of the model for the stated context of use.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-cfd-hemolysis-accepted",
